    <h1 class="title">
      <!----><a class="resource-link">RESOURCE_TYPE_LABEL: </a><span class="resource-name masthead-resource-title">RESOURCE_NAME</span><span class="badge-state bg-success badge-state"><!--v-if--><span class="msg">Active</span></span>
